The package boost-coroutine2 is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS coroutine2)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::coroutine2)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_coroutine2 REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::coroutine2)
